Achievements.Name: Street Hawk
Achievements.Description: Fill the Turbo bar and then use it all in one go without hitting anything.

Achievements.Name: Short and sweet
Achievements.Description: Unlock the Victors' Championship in at most 70 races.

Achievements.Name: What? More?
Achievements.Description: Earn at least 150,000 Kudos in the tournament.

Achievements.Name: Sponsored
Achievements.Description: Finish all the game missions at least once.

Achievements.Name: The King of shopping
Achievements.Description: Buy all of the game's motorcycles.

Achievements.Name: Jackpot
Achievements.Description: Earn at least 3,000 credits at the end of a race.

Achievements.Name: That much?!
Achievements.Description: Earn at least 5,000 credits at the end of a race.

Achievements.Name: Easy does it
Achievements.Description: Earn at least 200,000 points at the end of a race.

Achievements.Name: Stuntman
Achievements.Description: Earn at least 400,000 points at the end of a race.

Achievements.Name: Could do better
Achievements.Description: Earn at least 100,000 points with one combo.

Achievements.Name: Not bad...
Achievements.Description: Earn at least 200,000 points with one combo.

Achievements.Name: I'm back!
Achievements.Description: Finish a race at least one lap ahead of an opponent.

Achievements.Name: By a nose
Achievements.Description: Finish a race less than 0.1 s ahead of an opponent.

Achievements.Name: Ace
Achievements.Description: Finish first in the two rankings of a race.

Achievements.Name: Can't get worse
Achievements.Description: Finish a race in last place in the two rankings.

Achievements.Name: Comeback
Achievements.Description: Have at least 10 accidents and still be the fastest in the race.

Achievements.Name: Record holder
Achievements.Description: Complete a time trial on each of the game's circuits.

Achievements.Name: Is that all?
Achievements.Description: Finish 25 laps in a row in the same race.

Achievements.Name: We have a winner!
Achievements.Description: Finish an online race in first place.

Achievements.Name: We have a champion!
Achievements.Description: Come first in 5 online races in a row.

Achievements.Name: Enthusiast
Achievements.Description: Reach at least 180 minutes of race time.

Achievements.Name: Marathon
Achievements.Description: Reach at least 360 minutes of race time.

Achievements.Name: Over-connected
Achievements.Description: Reach at least 60 minutes of online race time.
